      <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>WHAT?</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>
              Combine two or more network interfaces into a single bonded device.
            </para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>WHY?</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>
              Network bonding can increase bandwidth and/or provide redundancy.
            </para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
